window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Jonathon Hunter is a long way from home and intent on getting back to track down his unknown adversary. But local problems intrude - an annoyance becomes a real threat. Trading one war for another wasn't in his game plan, but you do what has to be done to keep others alive. Jonathon isn't playing one of his computer games any more, and the save button only works by putting your life on the line.&nbsp;</p> <p>When the odds are stacked against you, there is only one thing left to do. <i>Send in the Hero.</i></p>"; 
